hackathon-description-text: MHacks Nano is our first ever online hackathon. Open to all students, Nano is your chance to start something new or continue working on that project you never quite had the time to finish and showcase it to the world. Form a team with up to three friends and use any and all resources at your disposal. The winners will be chosen by you, the hackers!
hackathon-eligibility:
Any student over the age of 13 is eligible to participate in MHacks Nano. Individuals and teams of up to 4 members may participate.

hackathon-judging-criteria.judging-criterion: All winners for MHacks Nano will be determined by community voting!

hackathon-description-header: Students from across the world come to MHacks to build amazing things, transform dreams into realities, and to meet others with the same level of passion to build their future. MHacks is for creators.
